Plans for 0.2.0
===============

  W = Work in progress
  D = Done
  P = Postponed
  N = Not to be implemented

  Implement spell-checking using PyEnchant
    [D] Script to test PyEnchant installation
    [ ] Outline general spell-checking strategy
    [ ] Optional import in gaupol (start script)
    [ ] Glade files for dialogs (Gedit!)
    [N] lib implementation (Not sensible, PyEnchant is the lib!)
    [ ] gui: Spell check dialog (wxSpellCheckerDialog.py!)
    [ ] gui: Settings dialog
    [ ] gui: delegate
    [ ] gui: Menu entry visibility
    [ ] Test error handling


